config EMUL_BMI270
    bool "Emulate a Bosch BMI270 accel/gyro (native_sim tests)"
    depends on EMUL && BMI270
    help
      SPI register-file emulator for the Bosch BMI270 IMU. Satisfies the
      upstream bmi270 driver's full init handshake (chip id, soft reset,
      config-file upload, INTERNAL_STATUS poll) and lets tests inject
      accel/gyro samples via the sensor emulator backend API
      (emul_sensor_backend_set_channel). Only useful on native_sim; can
      never be enabled in hardware builds because CONFIG_EMUL is off there.
